  <releases>
    <release version="2023.9.0-beta1" date="2023-09-02">
      <description translatable="no">
        <p>- Added a new web service to download lyrics for a song</p>
        <p>- Added support for opening a folder with Tagger from the file manager</p>
        <p>- Added a "Select All Files" button next to the search bar</p>
        <p>- Redesigned the Lyrics dialog in which only unsynchronized or synchronized lyrics can be used for a file and not both</p>
        <p>- Fixed an issue where some album art for some OPUS files were not read</p>
        <p>- Fixed an issue where Tagger would crash on Tag to Filename if the tag contained an invalid file name character</p>
        <p>- Fixed an issue where Tagger would marked files as unsaved even if there were no changes</p>
        <p>- Updated translations (Thanks everyone on Weblate!)</p>
      </description>
    </release>
  </releases>
